== Requirements ==
 * Ruby 1.8
 * rubygems
 * sinatra (gem)
 * activerecord (gem)
 * sqlite3 (gem)
 * markaby (gem)
 * rake (gem)
 * rack (gem)

== Installation and running ==
 * {{{rake}}} runs all the tests
 * {{{rake db:migrate}}} generates the database
 * {{{rake db:initial}}} populates the database with initial data (instructions and licensing information).
 * {{{rackup}}} runs rapidito, the wiki database, in http://localhost:9292.

== Source code ==
The latest development version is available in github at http://github.com/aurelianito/rapidito/tree/master.

